      • AES_NONCE

        public static final String AES_NONCE
        A nonce used for AES encryption. The nature of this use case requires the nonce to be constant. The nonce should be an ASCII string 16-bytes in length. If you specify a shorter string it will be padded; a longer string will be truncated.
